  "texts": [
    "This creates room for the development of novel algorithms, most especially, with the use of recent neural word embeddings.",
    "TM provides an automated and efficient way to synthesize literature over the time-consuming and labour-intensive manual approach (Asmussen and Møller 2019).",
    "Thus, it is worth deploying appropriately.",
    "As shown in Fig. 24 (in appendix), it is not surprising to see the increasing usage of TM for synthesizing literature across the years due to its benefit over traditional approach such as content or thematic analysis.",
    "At this stage, TM approach is not widely used in the scientometric community compared to the traditional approach which might be largely due to the programming and statistical knowledge required to fully utilise it."
  ]
